    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This collector-grade E46 M3 showcases the pinnacle of naturally aspirated BMW M-Division engineering. At its heart is the S54 3.2L straight-six, featuring six individual throttle bodies and a high-pressure Double VANOS system for optimized valve timing across the rev range. The power is transmitted through a precise Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox to the rear wheels via an M-Variable Differential Lock. This example has undergone exhaustive preventative maintenance, including documented rod bearing replacement, a complete VANOS overhaul, and structural subframe reinforcement. The suspension retains its factory kinematics with refreshed bushings and dampers, ensuring the legendary chassis balance is preserved. With a linear power delivery to its 8,000 RPM redline and surgical throttle response, this is a turnkey specimen for the discerning purist.",
