      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional vehicle that stands as a testament to meticulous ownership. This car is in showroom condition, having been exclusively garage-kept and professionally detailed on a monthly basis. The exterior paint retains a deep, mirror-like luster with absolutely no stone chips, swirl marks, or scratches. Inside, the cabin is a time capsule; the premium leather seats are firm with no bolster wear, the carpets are spotless, and it still carries that distinct new-car fragrance. Every button, sensor, and electronic feature operates with factory-spec precision. Mechanically, this vehicle is flawless, backed by a comprehensive service portfolio with all maintenance performed ahead of schedule at authorized dealerships. The engine bay is clean enough to eat off of, and the drive is whisper-quiet, tight, and responsive. Included are both original keys, the factory window sticker, and all original manuals. This is, without exaggeration, the finest example of this model currently on the market.",
